&lt;sup&gt;*First a disclaimer beforehand: the posted code snippets are all basic examples. You&#39;ll need to handle trivial `IOException`s and `RuntimeException`s like `NullPointerException`, `ArrayIndexOutOfBoundsException` and consorts yourself.*&lt;/sup&gt;

